'''Amigisc''' - '''AMIGISC (Association Initials in Portuguese) Association-Friends of Santa Cristina Group of Social and Civic Intervention''' was formed in September 2000. Its main goal is achieving a better development of the Civil Parish of [[Couto (Santa Cristina)|Santa Cristina do Couto]], in [[Santo Tirso]] Municipality, [[Porto]] District, [[Portugal]] in the areas of environment, health, formation, habitation and culture.

